WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.800
Greetings.

00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:47.700
I am the Caretaker, a powerful virtual
construct

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:51.379
created by the Eldan to monitor all
scientific experiments

00:00:51.379 --> 00:00:55.940
on the planet Nexus. *Nngah* Excuse 
my erratic behavior

00:00:55.940 --> 00:00:59.350
but it seems that I have developed
certain instabilities

00:00:59.350 --> 00:01:06.350
since the Eldan ABANDONED ME HERE long ago. 
I am responsible for analyzing the physical

00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:11.800
and mental WEAKNESSES of sentient organisms,

00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:18.000
such as yourselves. It is important that
I clearly understand the potential of my subjects

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:24.299
in order to best determine how
to ANNIHILATE THEM! Oh my.

00:01:24.299 --> 00:01:32.600
Are you ready? Then please step forward 
into this virtual adventure in order to begin.

00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:38.600
Don't be alarmed. The experience will be EXCRUCIATINGLY PAINFUL!

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:45.540
During your adventure, your group will be
subjected to a variety of climates,

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:52.500
environments, and situations all chosen
specifically to END YOUR PATHETIC EXISTENCE. 

00:01:52.500 --> 00:01:58.400
Success will require more than skill in 
combat. During your experience,

00:01:58.410 --> 00:02:02.310
you and your companions will be 
expected to make critical decisions

00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:08.259
the required both intelligence and
intuition. Choose well,

00:02:08.259 --> 00:02:14.500
and be rewarded. Choose poorly, 
AND BE DESTROYED!

00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:19.800
Every choice leads to a new eventuality,
and every eventuality a new choice,

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:22.200
and remember, THIS VIRTUAL 
WORLD IS MY TWISTED DOMAIN.

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:26.600
I MAKE THE RULES AND I DETERMINE THE SEVERITY OF YOUR PUNISHMENT.

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:32.000
And the best part? You can experience
them over... and over...

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:37.400
AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER AND OVER

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:41.500
again. Thank you for 
participating in this experiment.

00:02:41.540 --> 00:02:47.150
I have learned a great deal and I'm
certain that we will meet again

00:02:47.150 --> 00:02:50.500
VERY SOON...

